data.description: Better than a new build! Paid off solar , and landscaped backyard! Gorgeous single-level home with an extended 2-car garage and an  8 ft RV gate! Discover the desirable open floor layout filled with so much natural light, tile flooring, and direct access to the backyard. The impeccable kitchen provides built-in appliances, recessed & pendant lighting, granite counters, beautiful dark cabinet with pull out drawers, a pantry,  an island with a breakfast bar and under sink RO system. Freshly carpeted primary retreat, offering a pristine private bathroom w/dual sinks & a walk-in closet. The spacious backyard, with its covered patio & artificial turf, invites you to relax or have fun! Save on your utility bills with owned solar.
